  author: 權健
  language: lzh
  text: 山橋日暮少人行野店炊烟一抹橫緩轡微吟歸得得馬蹄隨處踏瑤瓊
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 冒雪山行
  author: 權健
  language: lzh
  text: 山橋日暮少人行。野店炊烟一抹橫。緩轡微吟歸得得。馬蹄隨處踏瑤瓊。
korean:
  title: 모설 산행
  author: 권건
  language: kor
  text: |-
    징검다리에 해 저물어 가는 사람 적어지고
    들 주점 땐 연기는 한 빛으로 퍼져 있다
    말고삐 늦추고는 가늘게 읊어 돌아올 제
    말굽이 이르는 곳에 흰 구슬을 밟은 듯이
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1460_010_0150&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Through Snow on the Mountain Path
  author: Gwon Geon
  language: eng
  text: |-
    As daylight fades on the mountain bridge, fewer travelers pass,
    Smoke from the country inn stretches across in a single stroke.
    Slackening my horse's rein, I hum a gentle tune on my return—
    Wherever the hoofbeats fall, as if treading on white jade.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The imagery of 'white jade' (瑤瓊) refers to snow, suggesting the pristine beauty of the snow-covered mountain path and evoking the classical association of jade with purity and refinement.
